data.description: Excellent 2 fam brick house. 2 bedroom apartment over a  2 bedroom apartment plus full  finished basement.  This home features hardwood floors, interior stairs, full finished basement, backyard and private parking.  This is the ultimate investment property or live in comfortably.  Ideal for family that want to share and still be private.  All apartments have their own separate entrances, but when you want to get together there are interior stairs so you don't have to go outside.  Everyone can enter the basement or not from their apartment and the backyard.  This home is light and airy when the sun spills in and it's so close to shopping and transportation and the highway all in minutes.  So, if you're looking for neighborhood and places of worship and restaurants this is the one.
